==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Freshly
<hw>Fresh"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a fresh manner; vigorously;
newly, recently; brightly; briskly; coolly; <as>as, <ex>freshly</ex>
gathered; <ex>freshly</ex> painted; the wind blows
<ex>freshly</ex>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Looks he as <xex>freshly</xex> as he did?</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Freshman</ent>⟦br⟧
